|YKODarkWind reboots periodically to clear out the junk from memory, catch
global code updates, reset once-per-boot areas and whatnot. When the
mud reboots, all equipment stored in guilds, shops, boats etc. will
disappear, as will ponies and similar helpers. Boats will not disappear,
nor will money on or your person or in the bank.

The |WKB"uptime" |YKOcommand shows how long DarkWind has been up since the last
reboot, and when the next scheduled reboot is. Unfortunately, sometimes
unscheduled reboots are necessary for a variety of reasons. Players will
not be compensated for any losses incurred due to reboots.
